Package com.example.qr_quest

Class Comment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.qr_quest.Comment
  • public class Comment
extends Object
    This class represents a comment made by a user on a QR code. It includes the user's name who made the comment and the comment's text. This class also provides a method to fill a list of comments for a given QR code, retrieved from a database.
